assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Anli International Co., Ltd. primarily engages in the development, production, assembly, and sale of various precision metal stamping and magnesium aluminum die casting in China and Taiwan. The company is also involved in the design, research, and development of electronic components, vehicle components, new metal materials, machine parts, communication equipment, and computer software; manufacture of fine blanking die products; inductance components; metal finishing activities; and installation of automated equipment, as well as in CNC processing business. It also provides automotive products, optical communication products, vision system application products, household products, and other products. The company's products are used in notebook PCs, tablet PCs, desktop PCs, cell phones, game consoles, portable devices, wearable devices, internet communications, and home appliances. It primarily serves the computers, communications, and consumer electronics industries. The company was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Grand Cayman, the Cayman Islands.
